metadata.description:
During c.2021 theartistROBEBERLE submitted an Open API request for a ©t.a.r.e. code creation outline for making a digital artwork. During early c.2022, some artist copyright friendly programming became available with almost exactly his request. 

Working between c.April2022 through c.October2022 Robert Eberle created thousands of iterations of his natural language created artworks.

In this Historically new artwork created with the code outline he has compiled those artworks into one fun new artwork.
